'''平板支撑'''（plank）又稱'''撐高'''、'''撐舉'''、'''棒式'''或'''撐平板'''，是一種[[等长运动|等长]]{{link-en|核心 (身體)|core (anatomy)|核心}}強度運動，會讓身體維持在一個費力的姿勢，且要維持相當一段時間。常見的平板支撑是前支撑，維持[[俯卧撑|俯卧撑]]的姿勢，身體重量由前臂、手肘及脚趾支持。

平板支撑也有一些變體，像是側支撑或是背支撑<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=5un2SO9VYaMC&pg=PA61&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=zWZ1TcXRBof2tgPH_KmyBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CEAQ6AEwAjgK#v=onepage&q=plank&f=false Knack Weight Training for Women: Step-by-Step Exercises for Weight Loss] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5un2SO9VYaMC&pg=PA61&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=zWZ1TcXRBof2tgPH_KmyBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CEAQ6AEwAjgK#v=onepage&q=plank&f=false |date=20170218064433 }}, Leah Garcia. pp. 57. quote:"Plank variations are abundant, and small changes increase the intensity of the exercise."</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=EZgOE9M6-LQC&pg=PA263&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=zWZ1TcXRBof2tgPH_KmyBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDkQ6AEwATgK#v=onepage&q&f=false Weight Training for Dummies] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=EZgOE9M6-LQC&pg=PA263&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=zWZ1TcXRBof2tgPH_KmyBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDkQ6AEwATgK#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20170218073947 }}, Liz Neporent, Suzanne Schlosberg, Shirley J. Archer. pp.263.</ref>。在[[彼拉提斯|彼拉提斯]]及[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]中常練習平板支撑（瑜伽中會稱為棒式），在像[[拳擊|拳擊]]或其他運動的練習也會用到<ref name="Chabut">[http://books.google.com/books?id=SMe1_tbTMbUC&pg=PT126&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=lmZ1TY34NYW6sAOU_bXEBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CD8Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q&f=false Core Strength For Dummies], LaReine Chabut. Quote:"It's used in all yoga sun salutations and other poses. It is also a Pilates-based exercise used in many of Joseph Pilates exercises..."</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=lVMoKIfhPlQC&pg=PA176&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=lmZ1TY34NYW6sAOU_bXEBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CFsQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q&f=false Pocket Guide to Fitness] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=lVMoKIfhPlQC&pg=PA176&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=lmZ1TY34NYW6sAOU_bXEBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CFsQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20170218073930 }} Louiza Patsis. pp.176. quote:"The "plank exercise" is used in Pilates classes."</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=rLhupek_BbEC&pg=PA260&dq=planking+exercise&hl=en&ei=lmZ1TY34NYW6sAOU_bXEBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDoQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q&f=false Kettlebells for Dummies], Sarah Lurie. pp.260. quote:"If you've done other exercises like yoga or Pilates before, you may be familiar with the plank position already."</ref><ref>''The Ultimate Fitness Boxing & Kickboxing Workout'', Ross O'Donnell, Trafford Publishing, 2005, ISBN 978-1-4120-6451-4</ref>。

平板支撑可以訓練腹部、背部及肩膀，鍛鍊到的肌肉有：
* 主要肌肉：[[豎脊肌|豎脊肌]]、[[腹直肌|腹直肌]]及{{link-en|腹横肌|transversus abdominis muscle}}{{Citation needed|date=2015-03}}。
* 輔助肌肉（增效肌/{{link-en|节段稳定肌肉|segmental stabilizers}}）：[[斜方肌|斜方肌]]、{{link-en|菱形肌|rhomboid muscles}}、[[旋轉肌群|旋轉肌群]]、前，内侧和后侧[[三角肌|三角肌]]、[[胸大肌|胸大肌]]、[[前鋸肌|前鋸肌]]、[[臀大肌|臀大肌]]、[[股四頭肌|股四頭肌]]及[[腓腸肌|腓腸肌]]{{Citation needed|date=2015-03}}。

側支撑鍛鍊到的肌肉有：
* 主要肌肉：{{link-en|腹横肌|transversus abdominis muscle}}、{{link-en|臀中肌|gluteus medius muscle}}及{{link-en|臀小肌|gluteus minimus muscle}}、{{link-en|髋关节内收肌群|adductor muscles of the hip}}、[[外斜肌|外斜肌]]及[[內斜肌|內斜肌]]{{Citation needed|date=2015-03}}。
* 輔助肌肉：臀大肌、股四頭肌及[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]{{Citation needed|date=2015-03}}。

根據[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]，平板支撑的最久紀錄是由美國退休老兵喬治·胡特（George Hood）於2020年達成，長達8小時15分15秒。事實上早在兩年前，胡特就已在一場由[[推動世界紀錄|推動世界紀錄]]（ASSIST World Records）舉辦的活動中創下10小時10分鐘10秒的平板支撐紀錄，但當時並沒有金氏世界紀錄的認證官在場，因此這筆紀錄並沒有被金氏世界紀錄收錄<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/27/us/marine-plank-record.html | title = He Held a Plank for More Than 8 Hours, Setting a Record | date = 2020-02-27 | author = Hauser, Christine | publisher = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]] | accessdate = 2020-03-15 | archive-date = 2020-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200313060428/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/27/us/marine-plank-record.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

